Author: Pessimistic_Sheep
Text: ahh that's so shitty of him, i'm sorry. whenever something like that happens to me my diet also goes completely out of whack for several days. but it's okay! it's only been a week and some, i doubt you gained much weight. and no matter how much you did you'll always have the time to get to where you wanna be. this is my first day back to restricting too after multiple fuck up days, and i'm super excited to get the body i want! good luck to you :)
